---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Jevan Goldsmith"
  description="A short introduction to Jevan Goldsmith, the archive he is building, and the themes behind his work."
  canonical="https://jevangoldsmith.com/about.html"
  pageType="AboutPage"
>
<main class="about-content">
        <div class="about-layout">
            <div class="about-col-images left">
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/profile/profile-360.avif 360w, /images/generated/profile/profile-520.avif 520w, /images/generated/profile/profile-720.avif 720w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/profile/profile-720.jpg" class="img-tall" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/profile/profile-360.jpg 360w, /images/generated/profile/profile-520.jpg 520w, /images/generated/profile/profile-720.jpg 720w" sizes="160px"></picture>
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.avif 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.avif 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.avif 720w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg" class="img-square" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.jpg 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.jpg 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg 720w" sizes="160px"></picture>
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/profile/profile-360.avif 360w, /images/generated/profile/profile-520.avif 520w, /images/generated/profile/profile-720.avif 720w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/profile/profile-720.jpg" class="img-wide" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/profile/profile-360.jpg 360w, /images/generated/profile/profile-520.jpg 520w, /images/generated/profile/profile-720.jpg 720w" sizes="160px"></picture>
            </div>
            <div class="about-sections">
                <section class="about-section">
                    <p class="section-eyebrow">The Story</p>
                    <h1 class="section-title">How I Got Here</h1>
                    <p class="section-text">After completing my degree in finance, I discovered that my interests extended far beyond spreadsheets and balance sheets. I became fascinated by how technology is reshaping industries, how great companies build lasting cultures, and how ideas can be communicated effectively through writing.</p>
                    <p class="section-text">Currently, I spend my time exploring the intersection of finance, real estate development, and technology. My approach is simple: stay curious, think critically, and share openly.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section" id="focus">
                    <p class="section-eyebrow">Focus</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Building Beautiful Products</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">My focus is on the craft of building things people actually want to use. Beautiful in the deep sense — products that are clear, considered, and respect the person on the other side of the screen.</p>
                    <p class="section-text">That means caring about the architectural decisions that shape a project years out, the small interactions that make a tool feel inevitable, and the writing that surrounds them. The intersection of finance, real estate development, and technology is where I do most of this work.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section" id="values">
                    <p class="section-eyebrow">Values</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Impact · Mastery · Adventure</h2>
                    <p class="section-text"><strong>Impact</strong> — choose the work that moves something forward in the world, even slightly. Avoid effort that's only legible as effort.</p>
                    <p class="section-text"><strong>Mastery</strong> — go deep before you go wide. The compounding returns of getting genuinely good at a small number of things are worth the patience.</p>
                    <p class="section-text"><strong>Adventure</strong> — leave time and money to chase the things you can't plan for. The best memories, friendships, and ideas live just past the edge of your itinerary.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section" id="stats">
                    <p class="section-eyebrow">Stats</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title">The Particulars</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">Australian, 183cm, based out of Queensland with regular stints abroad. Trained in finance, building in real estate and technology, writing about what I find useful along the way.</p>
                    <p class="section-text">If you want the longer version — what I'm reading, watching, working on, and thinking about — the rest of the site is the answer.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="about-col-images right">
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.avif 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.avif 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.avif 720w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg" class="img-square" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.jpg 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.jpg 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg 720w" sizes="160px"></picture>
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/logo/logo-nav-88.avif 88w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-176.avif 176w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-264.avif 264w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-352.avif 352w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/logo/logo-nav-352.png" class="img-square" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/logo/logo-nav-88.png 88w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-176.png 176w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-264.png 264w, /images/generated/logo/logo-nav-352.png 352w" sizes="160px" width="88" height="80"></picture>
                <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.avif 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.avif 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.avif 720w" sizes="160px"><img src="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg" class="img-tall" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="/images/generated/content/zen-nature-320.jpg 320w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-480.jpg 480w, /images/generated/content/zen-nature-720.jpg 720w" sizes="160px"></picture>
            </div>
        </div>
</main>
